## Attributes

- **`example`** (string): An example property

## Slots

- **default**: Default slot for component content

{{#if hasEvents}}
## Events

- **`{{componentName}}-change`**: Fired when the example changes. Detail: `{ example: string }`
- **`change`**: Standard change event
{{/if}}

